highlights: RESIDENTIAL  BUILDING for SALE  |INTERNATIONAL CITY PHASE 2|AFFORDABLE PRICE
desc: Properties Exchange proudly present you Residential Building B+G+4 for sale in one of the fastest developing area of Dubai,International City Phase 2, Warsan. 100% Ready with 80 units and indoor parking. 1 BHK from 570.5 to 845 sqf2BHK from 932.9 to 1205.6 sqfAl Warsan is a mixed-use area adjacent to the popular residential neighbourhood of International City. It is a relatively new development in the vicinity of Al Warqaa and Nad Al Sheba and is still undergoing construction. The community is further divided into four sub-districts named 1 to 4. Predominantly industrial, the locality is mainly known for housing the Dubai Sewage and Treatment Plant. However, it has an evolving residential side, also growing in popularity. A mixed-use residential communitySome parts of Warsan are freeholdIn the vicinity of International City, Al Warqa, Nad Al ShebaA blend of industrial and residential developmentOffers a wide range of residential properties including villas and flatsMost villas and apartments are comparatively newAffordable rental and freehold pricesHome to Warsan Lake and Desert Palm DubaiHOTELS IN AL WARSANMelia Desert Palm Dubai is a 5-star hotel in Warsan on Al Awir Road. The hotel has suites and villas equipped with modern amenities. Other features include a boutique fitness centre, Samana Spa, a wide range of casual dining restaurants and bars, events space, complimentary internet connectivity and much more. TRANSPORTATION AND PARKING SPACES IN AL WARSANThere are plenty of parking spaces in Al Warsan for residents and visitors. The industrial side has dedicated areas for the staff and the residential complexes have reserved parking spaces. Villas and townhouses also feature dedicated spaces with enough capacity for two cars. Residents can either travel by taxi or personal cars. There are quite a few RTA bus routes that connect the area to other parts of the city. The buses also connect to the Centrepoint Metro Station on the Red Line of the Dubai Metro that is 11-minutes away by car. Moreover, Dubai Municipality has just started providing free transport to the Central Fruits and Vegetable Market at Al Warsan for the convenience of buyers, workers and sellers. AMENITIES, SCHOOLS AND HEALTHCAREMost of the supermarkets in Al Warsan are concentrated in Al Warsan 3. This includes New Parsons Hypermarket, Madeena Supermarket, Warsan Al Madina Supermarket and more. Carrefour Hypermarket in Dragon Mart 2, Lulu Express in the France Cluster of International City and Ecity Supermarket in the Russia Cluster of International City are other popular supermarkets nearby. The nearest school to Warsan 4 International City is Ignite School. It follows the American curriculum and caters to both Emirati and expat children. It is also considered as one of the best schools in Al Warqa. Other nearby schools within closer proximity include GEMS School  and Repton School Dubai. Those seeking higher education in Dubai can head to the Manipal Academy of Higher Education around 6 minutes away. Other universities near Warsan 4 International City include Amity University which takes 9 minutes to reach and Heriot-Watt University at the same distance. Manipal and Amity are Indian-based higher education institutes, whereas, Heriot-Watt University is a UK-based university. FOR MORE DETAILS CONTACT: Fareeda
